snippet.title: Megaquarium: Freshwater Frenzy - Deluxe Expansion (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Freshwater Frenzy is the first Deluxe Expansion for Megaquarium. Including dozens of new fish, tanks and decorations, not to mention a challenging freshwater-focused campaign! Discover everything the freshwater habitat has to offer in this fully loaded expansion!

Wishlist the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1315300/Megaquarium_Freshwater_Frenzy__Deluxe_Expansion/

http://www.megaquariumgame.com
http://www.twitter.com/twicecircled
